title: WhatsApp Support 1.5.1 - WordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org More than 1 billion people in over 180 countries use WhatsApp. WhatsApp Support WordPress Plugin provides better and easy way to communicate visitors and customers directly to your support person. It runs on your own WordPress site, allowing you full control over your support via WhatsApp. WhatsApp Support WordPress Plugin Features Multi Person Support Single Person Support Group Invitation Fully Responsive Fully Customizable Schedule by Days Auto Popup with Sound Live Support Button Shortcode Generator Enable/Disable on Mobile Devices Enable/Disable on Desktops and Laptops Filter by Pages, Slugs
